abstract.para: A dataset containing all occurrences available in GBIF matching the query: { "and" : [ "TaxonKey is one of (Tracheophyta, Lepidoptera)", "BasisOfRecord is one of (Observation, Human Observation, Specimen)", "StateProvince is one of (Maryland)", "HasCoordinate is true", "Year 2001-2023" ] } The dataset includes records from the following constituent datasets. The full metadata for each constituent is also included in this archive: 2246 records from Delaware State University, Claude E.
